    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm absolutely thrilled to list this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it drives like a total dream. It\u2019s essentially flawless and ready for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. You really won't find one better cared for! Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
