    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade BMW E46 M3, presenting in concours-level condition. The S54B32 power plant delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, with the high-pressure Double VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced with coated shells for longevity. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh using OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Every seal, from the constant pressure valve to the valve cover, is bone dry. This is a mechanically transparent, high-revving masterpiece for the purist collector.",
